HEADWORD: Bullish
<hw>Bull"ish</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Partaking of the
nature of a bull, or a blunder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let me inform you, a toothless satire is as improper as a toothed
sleek stone, and as <qex>bullish</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bullist</ent>⟦br⟧
